    <h2>General Extension</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Live server - Displays Live record on browser on save</li>
      <li>Prettier - Format Code Alignment Especially on copy paste</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Install prettier</li>
        <li>Go to vscode settings</li>
        <li>Type Fomat on -> Tick Format on save and Format on Paste</li>
        <li>Type Default Formatter -> Change to Prettier Code Format</li>
      </ul>
      <li>
        Auto Rename tag -Automatically change close tag similar to open tag
